>             checkCVSVersion();
We can expand this to both detect incompatible versions (1.10, 1.11, 1.11.1) and 
versions we don't support (CVSNT) and print an appropriate message for each 
case.

We do not want to perform this on every connection. Instead we should put it in 
the connection validation code which gets run once when the location is ceated. 
The only down side to this is that the user may disable this option.
Fixed.

